sheep.gui
Class Widget

java.lang.Object
  sheep.gui.Widget
All Implemented Interfaces:
KeyboardListener, TouchListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
Container, TextButton
public abstract class Widget
extends java.lang.Object
implements KeyboardListener, TouchListener

The superclass of all components in the GUI system. A Widget can be objects like a button, a list or textfield. Each Widget can also trigger events, which classes conforming to the WidgetListener iterface can listen to.
